       This  is  a  new version of dd..rrggbb, which sends the data to the graphics
       monitor in true-color RGB format.  Unlike the previous version, it does
       not  attempt to quantize the combined image into a fixed number of col-
       ors.  Nor does it have an option to generate a  composite  layer.   The
       image  and  raster map layers will not display properly if the graphics
       device does not have a reasonable sampling of the RGB color-space.


